<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="early-adj">early <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɜːli/    美 /'ɜːrli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>早的；提早的；早期的；最先的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please reply <strong>at your earliest convenience</strong>. 
请尽早回复。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He died suddenly <strong>in his early 50s</strong>. 
他刚50出头就突然去世了。</p><footer>2011 湖南</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The early bird catches the worm. 
早起的鸟儿有虫吃。/先下手为强。</p></div></div>